web 3: (2021-) cont. New communities are being created at a rapidly accelerating rate around different interests and niches, anyone can do it. Web3 is facilitating natural human social behaviour and this is why it‚Äôs not going anywhere!

web 3: (2021-) you consume, create and own content by leveraging blockchain technology to create digital assets. Now the content creator gets paid, the artist gets paid, the developer gets paid - participation & effort is rewarded.

web 2: (2005 - 2020) you consumed and created content. The ownership was in the hands of large organisations like Google, Apple, Facebook & Amazon but we happily participated as this was our only way into a digital community.
web 1: (1990-2005) you consumed content, you were happy - this was revolutionary.
